title: 10 Takeaways from Week 13
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 13
description:
Daniel Jeremiah & Rhett Lewis recap Week 13 of the NFL season, including the Texans big win over the Patriots (1:50), Ryan Tannehill’s Titans resurgence (5:30), the Bengals getting their first win (10:50), Bucs defeating the Jaguars (14:30), the Eagles struggle again (19:30), Steelers defense keeping them in playoff race (22:45), Drew Lock’s debut win (26:45), Rams offense shows life (30:30). Bucky Brooks joins the show, from London, to give his takes on the Ravens looking like a Super Bowl team (33:10) and the Chiefs offense resembling the Houston Rockets (37:40).
